{"tid":333562,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"今年回報70%，最大回調14.7%，你問我答。","createTime":"2017-07-24T02:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T06:10:18.000Z","uid":130720,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c46218ef93802c72d53f6de81609a5bbf7c1cdfa","tid":333562,"uid":130720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:14:56.000Z","msg":"我用程式交易加人手交易港期，回報暫時錄得70%，最大回調14.7%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/24/100425_f13d8c0817094f3e9b9552b4614e8166.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2F100425_f13d8c0817094f3e9b9552b4614e8166.PNG&h=3fa7b0af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果想知道更多關於程式交易，可入我個fb page去了解更多:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bettertrading.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbettertrading.hk%2F&d=XYhUiEuAbtPYRjPsqohspjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=c11dbb55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bettertrading.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"8222332f9cc9dfba1031a3725d9f646cdbcb9eb9","tid":333562,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:17:53.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"6d0e222bf405bfa7518afda66fa105181eafe2df","tid":333562,"uid":104179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:19:06.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"52f2848357189284557c79001f87bf65dc4df2a0","tid":333562,"uid":125799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:27:02.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"36039f2d9f285ca4d0f79a0f429f6bed0a3fe701","tid":333562,"uid":130720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:29:29.000Z","msg":"講一下我對交易既睇法，點先會賺到錢:<br />\n<br />\n1）穩定的經濟基礎。基本的現金流，打工仔同租金收入都得，總之一定要每月都有收入，炒唔店果陣，份工就係救生衣。<br />\n<br />\n2）生存能力，即係風險管理。有左現金流，其實會有較清晰的頭腦，壓力也較低。先訂立可輸既錢（稱R)，隨你。總之夠你連輸20-30次都仲可以繼續交易就得，呢個數愈多愈好，我個人計，即使連輸100次都仲生存到，只要有一次贏錢就可大幅cover輸既錢。<br />\n<br />\n3）方法，個市點行唔太重要，將來升同跌對你係無關係。重點係你點操作，由你既pnl話返你知你係做岩定做錯。輸到你先訂立輸既金額就要走，唔好諗，等下次機會。用咩方法都好，總有機會會贏錢，如果你無贏過，一定係交易太密先會咁，你用平均線都唔會次次輸。如果你做岩方向，呢個就係關鍵，賺到你1-2個R就加注，總之加到一個位係呢個交易最差係平手就可以。幾時離場？無標準。我做法係當賬面賺到10000，利潤回到5000就走。概念係咁，無一定。<br />\n<br />\n以上三點你做到唔代表你一定賺，但當你向住呢個方向行，你慢慢會拿捏到炒股炒期個概念，其實大同小異，長遠就會獲利，賺多賺少真係睇你風險承受既能力係幾多。要係金融市場賺錢，先將你所識既方法放低，從來無一個方法係穩定，只有操作，紀律同心態先可以穩定。"},{"pid":"943da367323188cfae741a1cb16408765947ce9c","tid":333562,"uid":53090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:39:37.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"4e6364b6b4e65ae43d3fc9c05c1d2aadb8a6b6de","tid":333562,"uid":16101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:45:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b02c68cecfbd96651fe233f34eed992da18e846","tid":333562,"uid":28472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e748bfca5239ed869dd61658cadaeeedddca74","tid":333562,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:48:35.000Z","msg":"呢D市, 亞豬亞狗都賺啦, 炒期先得70%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n買中隻175, 都幾倍啦"},{"pid":"2cfe91c3e29a36dae3d43aa00991014e50369ce0","tid":333562,"uid":12609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:52:04.000Z","msg":"又賣廣告<br />\n咁好賺做咩要益人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea4e199ca8a6d95c4387433ce345ee81e71831b","tid":333562,"uid":130720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:57:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢D市, 亞豬亞狗都賺啦, 炒期先得70%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n買中隻175, 都幾倍啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講得岩，對於很多人，我回報不值一提。不過只想拋磚引玉，可大家交流下，令大家技術可提升，話時話，師兄對選股有咩高見？"},{"pid":"c6823e7bfff943d80672aa63d81972244821ad13","tid":333562,"uid":130720,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:57:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>