>\n<br />\n無收你錢wor，點解師兄咁講？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連登真無好多低質人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近排我都用multichart同ib實時test緊，師兄有無興趣留低tg傾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有個group 討論algo trading<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DPFsRgmbvPub0LLHk6hWDg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDPFsRgmbvPub0LLHk6hWDg&d=XYhUiEuAbtPYRjPsqohspjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5d57f99f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DPFsRgmbvPub0LLHk6hWDg</a>"},{"pid":"8ccaea90ca63f82930039a475b4e50ea68f960ed","tid":333562,"uid":126053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:34:12.000Z","msg":"17 年keep住賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係依家得30%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e7069617b96d9db7370130749294418e478bdd","tid":333562,"uid":38172,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢D市, 亞豬亞狗都賺啦, 炒期先得70%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n買中隻175, 都幾倍啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n程式交易既重點唔在於人手交易而係自動交易啊<br />\n如果你訓係到都有70%回報，有乜野可以做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我咪講左&quot;呢D&quot;市況囉, 唔洗電腦, 就咁BUY AND HOLD都有賺<br />\n<br />\n你個SYSTEM跟本經唔起風浪"},{"pid":"04d22379e7e07a94a349360d6ee0e0fe7611b7b3","tid":333562,"uid":130720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打用咩平台trade 最好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無咩所謂，我用開multichart，最重要都係個交易框架。"},{"pid":"03ca83a794c6268917347010dc2f42eefae19567","tid":333562,"uid":130720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋師兄你條equity curve只係得後半後賺錢，所以小心啵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我程式係做day trade，頭半年都無咩大波動，都好正常賺唔到咩錢。"},{"pid":"43b5d63300121955eed824bc9ad72c838753dddf","tid":333562,"uid":130720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:38:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Software成本幾錢？<br />\n如果本身0 programme 知識，係咪好難先寫到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔算太難，multichart 個easy language 都易上手。"},{"pid":"5324e47fbbf81ad42596b3b133c2d341b0227aab","tid":333562,"uid":43841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:39:17.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"17adddfaec0a6d2d2bcafd23b665b18c19efbfc0","tid":333562,"uid":130720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>17 年keep住賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係依家得30%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n市場俾幾多自己賺唔會知，生存到市場才是最重要。生存唔到，下年有幾好既機會都捕捉唔到。"},{"pid":"c4f328e6113f63325c0e7463a3b21a217dbc0873","tid":333562,"uid":38172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:40:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同埋師兄你條equity curve只係得後半後賺錢，所以小心啵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我程式係做day trade，頭半年都無咩大波動，都好正常賺唔到咩錢。</blockquote><br />\n你得一年都無既貨仔就算啦, KEEP到5年再開POST威威啦 到時我話你勁<br />\n<br />\n我有跟過D台仔程式交易員既紀錄, 我見到KEEP住幾年都有錢賺, 但都因為佢話頂唔住有時MAX LOSS太大而關閉, 無再用<br />\n<br />\n仲要今年咁易炒, 你有無做BACK TEST架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4142a92372992d7cc68bff29e67ccf7749bb8393","tid":333562,"uid":130720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:53:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同埋師兄你條equity curve只係得後半後賺錢，所以小心啵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我程式係做day trade，頭半年都無咩大波動，都好正常賺唔到咩錢。</blockquote><br />\n你得一年都無既貨仔就算啦, KEEP到5年再開POST威威啦 到時我話你勁<br />\n<br />\n我有跟過D台仔程式交易員既紀錄, 我見到KEEP住幾年都有錢賺, 但都因為佢話頂唔住有時MAX LOSS太大而關閉, 無再用<br />\n<br />\n仲要今年咁易炒, 你有無做BACK TEST架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5年就無，不過我交易左3年了