n係咪全職？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係全職，用10萬計3張左右，但睇情況，可能會多可能會少。</blockquote><br />\n都幾博～ 恆指既話十幾倍槓桿～</blockquote><br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，應該冇十倍"},{"pid":"4d9d603702fe5f96610a815d4a1e51ad7daf68fa","tid":333562,"uid":130720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T03:14:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同埋師兄你條equity curve只係得後半後賺錢，所以小心啵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我程式係做day trade，頭半年都無咩大波動，都好正常賺唔到咩錢。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無知一問，只係向上升算唔算大波動? 睇返vix 年頭仲高過而家喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你睇返aastock過去3-5年，而家波幅指數係創緊新低。今年同2015年比係差好遠。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但睇返條equity curve，主要賺都係2017年5月尾起<br />\n<br />\n姐係波幅愈嚟愈細， &quot;無咩大波動，都好正常賺唔到咩錢&quot;，但係條curve 又賺到錢，姐係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n利潤來自over night position，少量day trade。<br />\n今年年頭覺得做daytrade 唔店，先加埋overnight，最後好彩都做岩左決定。"},{"pid":"5dfabae116cdf063b7921d2015d9c79bc227df76","tid":333562,"uid":130720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T03:16:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>70%係建基於咩數？按金？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基於我9成本金，1成係存款加少量股票。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我每賺多3萬就加碼一張細國指～ 樓主一張細期同資金比例係幾多？<br />\n<br />\n係咪全職？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係全職，用10萬計3張左右，但睇情況，可能會多可能會少。</blockquote><br />\n都幾博～ 恆指既話十幾倍槓桿～</blockquote><br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，應該冇十倍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYes，無10倍。我唔會下下交易都出動哂所有策略。"},{"pid":"c1cc54f1386a6e39286b7b303a812e28f3c4599f","tid":333562,"uid":20213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:50:34.000Z","msg":"Multichart自動交易係咪淨係支援部分券商？一通得唔得？"},{"pid":"1f46f1a442cb071bb4d3d8811191e503f66cffe2","tid":333562,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>multichart 定amibroker好？ <br />